ine#Suwa Myōjin (Zama)|ja|石楯尾神社#諏訪明神 (座間市入谷)|lt=Suwa Myōjin (Zama)|lt_ja=諏訪明神}} || Kanagawa Prefecture Zama City 入谷 || |- | ({{ill|candidate shrine|de|Kandidatenschrein|ja|論社|1=candidate shrines|2=ja|3=論社|lt=candidate|zh|論社}}) {{ill|Ishitateo Shrine#Imperial Shrine Site|ja|石楯尾神社#皇大神宮 (藤沢市)|lt=Imperial Shrine Site|lt_ja=皇大神宮}}境内末社 || Fujisawa City 鵠沼 || |}
